Package: cockpit-sensors
Name: Cockpit Sensors
Description: Cockpit module that displays hardware sensors (temperatures, fans, voltages and power) reported by hwmon, lm-sensors, RAPL, NVMe and SMART.
Author: bryamzxz <bryamestebanvargas@gmail.com>
Maintainer: bryamzxz <bryamestebanvargas@gmail.com>
Version: %{VERSION}
Depends: cockpit-bridge
Recommends: lm-sensors, nvme-cli, smartmontools
Architecture: all
Homepage: https://github.com/bryamzxz/cockpit-sensors
